query_results.description: Find all people with phone numbers containing '555'
query_results.query: SELECT person_id, full_name, phone FROM people WHERE phone LIKE '%555%'

query_results.description: Check which of these people own cats
query_results.query: SELECT p.full_name, pet.name, pet.species FROM people p JOIN pets pet ON p.person_id = pet.owner_id WHERE p.phone LIKE '%555%' AND pet.species = 'Cat'

query_results.description: Verify there is exactly one cat owned by people with '555' in their phone number
query_results.query: SELECT COUNT(*) as cat_count FROM pets WHERE species = 'Cat' AND owner_id IN (SELECT person_id FROM people WHERE phone LIKE '%555%')
